We made a quantum leap in 2025 — and now we’re scaling fast.
That’s why we’re looking for a Growth Product Manager with 4+ years of experience to help us build and execute growth strategies, run experiments (including A/B tests), and drive key product metrics.


WHO WE ARE:

Zeely AI is an all-in-one AI marketing platform that helps small businesses and marketing teams grow and achieve their business goals.
With the power of AI, we enable users to create high-quality ad creatives, UGC videos, viral content, banners, and launch effective paid & organic campaigns on Facebook and Instagram.

In simple terms:
We’ve made the world’s best AI marketing tools — previously доступні only to large brands with big budgets — accessible to everyone.



YOUR MISSION

You'll be responsible for identifying and validating new growth opportunities for both the product and the business.

Your responsibilities will include:

 - Researching new markets, customer segments, and ICPs;

 - Discovering new product use cases;

 - Generating, prioritizing, and validating product hypotheses;

 - Launching experiments and MVPs;

 - Analyzing results and scaling successful initiatives;

 - Working cross-functionally with Product, Marketing, Analytics, and Engineering;

 - Identifying the company's next major growth opportunities.


WHAT WE'RE LOOKING FOR

 - 4+ years of experience as a Growth Product Manager, Product Manager, Growth Marketing Manager, or Product Marketing Manager in a product company;

 - Proven experience launching new products, business lines, or growth initiatives (0→1 or scaling after achieving product-market fit);

 - Experience researching new markets, customer segments, and growth opportunities;

 - Hands-on experience running product experiments and A/B tests;

 - Strong product thinking and strategic mindset;

 - Deep understanding of customer journeys and product funnels;

 - Experience working with analytics platforms such as Mixpanel, Amplitude, Tableau, Google Analytics, or similar;

 - Experience defining requirements and collaborating with engineering teams;

 - Understanding of monetization models and unit economics;

 - Strong data-driven decision-making skills;

 - High ownership and the ability to independently identify problems and drive initiatives forward;

 - Upper-Intermediate English or higher.


NICE TO HAVE

 - Experience in AI, SaaS, or mobile products;

 - Experience designing or launching new business or monetization models;

 - Experience expanding into new markets or customer segments;

 - Experience managing large marketing budgets;

 - Experience working in a product-led growth or experimentation-driven environment.



NUMBERS THAT SPEAK LOUDER THAN WORDS:

— 4 years on the market → stable, profitable company backed by top-tier international investors
— 4× growth over the past year
— 1,000,000+ businesses already use Zeely (and growing fast every day)
— Top-3 in our category in the US market
— 150+ team members
— Markets: US + worldwide

We are not a startup searching for product-market fit.
We are a proven business with massive potential — scaling what already works.
And we’re looking for someone who can accelerate this growth.






WHY IT’S EXCITING TO WORK WITH US:

— Work with cutting-edge AI (LLMs, content generation, automation) 🤖 in a product with 1M+ users and rapid growth (4× YoY) 📈
— Direct impact on revenue and business growth → this is a core growth role
— Strong ownership: influence strategy, product roadmap, and decision-making
— Freedom to experiment 🚀: new channels, formats, hypotheses
— Fast iteration cycle: idea → test → result → scale
— Combination of performance + organic growth
— Work with Tier-1 markets, large budgets, and real data
— Strong team that supports your growth
— Remote-first 💻 (with offices in Warsaw & Kyiv if preferred)
— Regular performance reviews, days off / sick leave, FOP support



HIRING PROCESS:

Recruiter interview → Head of Product Growth interview → Test task

